Text: WMIC RTO Seams TF Report on RTO Scheduling Timelines RTOWest Vick Kasarjian CaISO Mike Raezer Desert Star Attached is a transmittal letter and report from the WMIC RTO Seams TF for your RTOs review and comment To facilitate discussion at the August WMIC meeting we would like to receive comments from each RTO by August The first attached file is the Transmittal letter and Report The other files are attachments to the Report These are timeline charts and should be printed on legal size paper using a color printer Let me know if you have any questions Dean
